{"tid":1978382,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"每次聽黨衛軍話「有人犯法就拉」都令人諗起7.21","createTime":"2020-04-18T16:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T16:56:04.000Z","uid":21470,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e5224b6d57a13c438c17af64ad8aa6475f478e4f","tid":1978382,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:10:40.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強：警方執法不偏不倚不理會被捕人背景身份<br />\n18.04.2020 21:50<br />\n<br />\n警方拘捕多名民主派人士，涉嫌在去年組織或參與未經批准的遊行集會。警務處處長鄧炳強晚上見記者時表示，警方作出拘捕及檢控是基於充分證據，強調警方執法不偏不倚、無畏無懼，不會理會被捕人的背景身份，是否有權勢、是否能控制傳媒以抹黑孤立警隊及煽動仇恨等。被問到警方行動是否與中聯辦及港澳辦就泛民議員的發言有關，鄧炳強指警方的行動和部分人士的發言無關，重申只要有人犯法就會執法，無論時隔多久都會深入調查。他指，3宗案件涉及很多不同人物 ，當中部分人牽涉相同及多宗的案件或罪行，指今日作大規範拘捕是正常合理做法，與臨近去年「612」一周年無關。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強指，留意到有被捕人士將犯法的責任推給政府，令很多年輕人被鼓動，香港整體守法意識降低，情況令他擔憂。他說，其中一名在法律界有相當崇高地位的被捕人士，指對與年輕人一同被捕感到光榮，他對此感到非常擔憂及驚訝，認為資深的法律界人士應勸籲年輕人守法，但對方竟然鼓動年輕人繼續犯法，認為對方不應感到驕傲，而是應感到羞恥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281863&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1281863%26csid%3D261_341&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDmg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=28c50f5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281863&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"1f757a758665d7f6d86407fef8a96a78da9c5016","tid":1978382,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flih.kg%2F1870807&h=dc6c0b62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35ad729632fab0c7efc853d0cbd5a72af50ab24d","tid":1978382,"uid":89349,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDU58B7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDU58B7.jpg&h=2764b124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3537626032d3bf7264075999f6c2220feae7a96d","tid":1978382,"uid":2507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:13:44.000Z","msg":"黨衛軍犯法點算？望不見紐倫堡法庭嘅存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb3cc3093cc6cf7c3e306bd5cafae6434e3020d","tid":1978382,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:32:20.000Z","msg":"原來無犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451ebd9c22ef4161c4b8c96cec942fc5b27e9de9","tid":1978382,"uid":145273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:42:56.000Z","msg":"佢每次講依一句就大巴大巴咁車落去佢自己埋面度"},{"pid":"0739a359219b43e62e77a9adb14dd5522a5e3fe7","tid":1978382,"uid":126366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:45:29.000Z","msg":"依條狗賊已經一早練到講大話完全唔會斬眼<br />\n白痴先會信佢講嘢"},{"pid":"4ddf0d58362dbba846d0b2a92b481c6bc3c991f7","tid":1978382,"uid":145273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0739a359219b43e62e77a9adb14dd5522a5e3fe7","tid":1978382,"uid":126366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:45:29.000Z","msg":"依條狗賊已經一早練到講大話完全唔會斬眼<br />\n白痴先會信佢講嘢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"仲勁過盧偉聰，嗰個連膊頭同心口都唔識分嘅一哥"},{"pid":"afa6468a30c21d3089d3e66e67458c1fd315e881","tid":1978382,"uid":245033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:49:57.000Z","msg":"所以721真係班仆街嘅大死穴"},{"pid":"020698d0bd2982f508b7a447852567f74e4dcbd9","tid":1978382,"uid":184756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"鄧狗得個講字，太監都不如"},{"pid":"8ee551623485d6f1d0bedcc386a48c21ce30a5cb","tid":1978382,"uid":18177,"like":0,"dislike":0